text: 2016 Emmy Awards may refer to: * 68th Primetime Emmy Awards, the 2016 Emmy Awards ceremony that honored primetime programming during June 2015 - May 2016 * 43rd Daytime Emmy Awards, the 2016 Emmy Awards ceremony that honored daytime programming during 2015 * 44th International Emmy Awards, the 2016 ceremony that honored international programming Category:Emmy Award ceremonies by year
